org.glassfish.jersey.client.rx

Interface RxInvocationBuilder<RX extends RxInvoker>

  • Type Parameters:
    RX - the concrete reactive invocation type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    javax.ws.rs.client.Invocation.Builder, javax.ws.rs.client.SyncInvoker

    public interface RxInvocationBuilder<RX extends RxInvoker>
extends javax.ws.rs.client.Invocation.Builder
    A reactive client request invocation builder.

    The builder is enhanced with two methods in addition to the invocation builder from JAX-RS, rx() and rx(java.util.concurrent.ExecutorService), giving access to reactive invoker that provide means to invoke reactive client requests.

    Since:
    2.13
    Author:
    Michal Gajdos, Marek Potociar (marek.potociar at oracle.com)
    See Also:
    Invocation.Builder, RxInvoker
